 Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705187,"age":22,"year":"1215","julianDay":2164830,"title":"Magna Carta","description":"King John of England agreed to a charter of rights called the Magna Carta. The document was originally drafted by the Archbishop of Canterbury to establish peace between King John and a group of rebel barons. The Magna Carta was completed in 1215 and is now considered to be one of the greatest constitutional documents of all time.","url":"https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/education/medieval/magna-carta/","urlTitle":"National Archives - Magna Carta","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Robert Chandos was born in 1193, in Snodhill, Herefordshire, England, his father, Walter de Chandos, was 33 and his mother, Mrs Walter de Chandos, was 27. He married Sarah Belet about 1209. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died before 23 October 1220."},"et":{"1193–before 23 October 1220":"1193–enne 23. oktoobrit 1220","1193–1220":"1193–1220","1193–Female":"1193–Surnud","1210–1232":"1210–1232","1160–Male":"1160–Surnud","1167–Female":"1167–Surnud","1215":"1215","before 23 October 1220":"enne 23. oktoobrit 1220","1167":"1167","1210":"1210","1232":"1232","1220":"1220","1193":"1193","ABT 1191":"umbes 1191","1160":"1160","ABT 1209":"umbes 1209","Snodhill, Herefordshire, England":"Snodhill, Herefordshire, England","Peterchurch, Herefordshire, England":"Peterchurch, Herefordshire, England","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1193–before 23 October 1220":"1193–ennen vuotta 23. lokakuuta 1220","1193–1220":"1193–1220","1193–Female":"1193–Kuollut","1210–1232":"1210–1232","1160–Male":"1160–Kuollut","1167–Female":"1167–Kuollut","1215":"1215","before 23 October 1220":"ennen vuotta 23. lokakuuta 1220","1167":"1167","1210":"1210","1232":"1232","1220":"1220","1193":"1193","ABT 1191":"noin 1191","1160":"1160","ABT 1209":"noin 1209","Snodhill, Herefords